Package notecontext

Class KeySignature

java.lang.Object
notecontext.KeySignature
public class KeySignature
extends java.lang.Object
Overview - represents the key signature of the current music sheet Purpose - you can ask the current key signature, and also ask if a particular note is chromatic or not to the current key signature UseCase - this will be instantiated in NoteContext, based on the keySignature value in Config.
